He wants to take you all sorrow and give you new life. You are a power in the hands of God and you know it !! Do not let the world you away from him , because he cares for you . Chapter-1
My Dream Girl
Do you believe in destiny? If yes it is okay but if you don’t believe then this story will surely change your concepts because this a real evidence of destiny, a living evidence.
My story begin when I was in 6th std. Till that time my life goes quite naturally but that days makes a lot of change in me. Just like every guys in my age I also feel some sort of attraction to a girl, but “what special from others is” she is only my ‘dream girl’.
Every day she comes into my dreams. She sat beside me, talk with me and even laugh with me. That makes me start loving nights more than my days. I patiently put of the days for my beautiful nights. In that way my three years has been gone and I became a 9th grade student. 
From my childhood I like to read science fictions and magazines, one day when I was looking through the pages of a magazine a face suddenly struck me. With no time I identify that she is the same girl who comes in my dreams because I can’t forget her beautiful eyes, sizzling smile and floating feathery hair more over her face has been already scribed in my heart.
Is that hard for finding an angel even if she is in a crowd? No, and I just find her and I just put the magazine of and start dancing and jump like a crazy monkey as i at least found ‘she is not only my dream girl but also she is living in the same world where I am living’. My happiness at that time where uncontrollable and my cells and body become super energetic than ever and at that time I even lift a 100 kg.
After some moment I eagerly pick up the magazine and pick the page I see her. Its an article concerning students findings in mathematics, one of the craziest subject I ever hate in my childhood. I read each and every word in that article carefully. Hurray!!! finally I did find her name. !! .
“ Ishana” my dream girl. I said her name along with me just like a 3 year child studying a word
“Ishana.Prajwol” its really matching too. I thank my mom for putting me such a name which is very much matching with her.
I take her photo in the magazine in my mobile cam and keep watching it day and night. My love for her keep increasing day by day and started to think of how to get her as mine. This really get affected in my studies and failures in examination become my partner, everyone started asking me “what is going on in my mind?” teasing from my parents became my daily routine.
At last I understand something that “just dreaming and simply watching will not gain me anything” so I decided to take some strong decisions, for that I need some perfect planning. I spend the next few days for life planning. Its really crazy that a 14 year boy planning about his life. But I don’t take it as a matter, I just make a perfect plan. As a part of my plan I decided to study maths as it is her favorite subject. So i started going for extra classes and spend much time in studies than dreaming. Even though I put her photo in front of me as it’s the only motivating thing that leads my life.
Days passed and my 9th grade annual examination has started. Every day I go for examination after seeing her and the day will surely a wonderful one after seeing his smiling face. At last I completed my 9th examination and it’s the time for enjoyment!! Yah my vacation has started. In this vacation I have some plans in my mind which has to be done. I heard girls love music, as my voice is not so sweet I quit singing and join in violin classes as it is the master instrument which makes strong feelings in mind. I am little bubbly at that time, how a sweet girl like a bubbly guy so I started going for body building center for making my body strong and fit. Sometimes during the pains in my hard work, I even think how crazy I am for doing these kind of things for a girl I have never seen in my life. I don’t even know where she is and what she is doing or did I ever get a chance to meet her. These all thoughts makes so much cracks in my mind but I never give up.
I strongly believe that every work has surely a result. I know god will surely gives a way.so I continue to work with my plan. After one month my 9th grade result has come and I got 90% marks in all subject, now everyone who tease me has started to say good about me. They don’t know the reason behind my success is Ishana.
this is just the review of first chapter.

Odpowiedzi

Czerwony ? twoje życie jest pełne miłości.
Czarny ? jesteś konserwatywna /y i agresywna /y.
Zielony ? twoja dusza jest zrelaksowana i jesteś osobą na luzie.
Niebieski ? jesteś spontaniczna /y i kochasz całusy i pieszczoty tych, których kochasz.
Żółty- jesteś bardzo szczęśliwą osobą i udzielasz dobrych rad tym, którzy są w dołku.

3. Jeżeli pierwsza litera twojego imienia jest:

A-K - masz w sobie dużo miłości, którą ofiarujesz bliskim i przyjaciołom.

L-R - Próbujesz cieszyć się życiem na maxa a twoje życie uczuciowe wkrótce rozkwitnie.

S-Z - lubisz pomagać innym a twoje przyszłe życie uczuciowe wygląda bardzo dobrze.

4. Jeśli urodziłaś /eś się w:

Styczeń ? Marzec
Rok minie ci bardzo dobrze i odkryjesz, że zakochasz się w kimś zupełnie nie oczekiwanym.

Kwiecień - czerwiec
Twój związek (uczuciowy) jest bardzo silny, będzie trwał długo i pozostawi wspaniałe wspomnienia na zawsze.

Lipiec- wrzesień
Będziesz mieć wspaniały rok i doświadczysz dużą zmianę w życiu na lepsze.

Październik ? grudzień
Twoje życie uczuciowe nie będzie zbyt wspaniałe, ale w końcu odnajdziesz swoją bratnią duszę.

5. Jeśli wybrałaś /eś

Czarny: twoje życie obierze inny kierunek, co będzie dla ciebie bardzo korzystne i bardzo cię to ucieszy.

Biały : Będziesz mieć przyjaciela, któremu można będzie całkowicie zaufać i zrobiłby dla ciebie wszystko, ale ty możesz sobie z tego nie zdawać sprawy.

6. Ta osoba jest twoim najlepszym przyjacielem.

7. To jest ilość twoich bliskich przyjaciół w twoim życiu.

8. Jeśli wybrałaś /eś:

Jezioro: Jesteś lojalnym przyjacielem i kochanką /iem.

Morze: Jesteś bardzo spontaniczna /y i lubisz zadowalać ludzi.

Chapter-1
My Dream Girl
Do you believe in destiny? If yes it is okay but if you don’t believe then this story will surely change your concepts because this a real evidence of destiny, a living evidence.
My story begin when I was in 6th std. Till that time my life goes quite naturally but that days makes a lot of change in me. Just like every guys in my age I also feel some sort of attraction to a girl, but “what special from others is” she is only my ‘dream girl’.
Every day she comes into my dreams. She sat beside me, talk with me and even laugh with me. That makes me start loving nights more than my days. I patiently put of the days for my beautiful nights. In that way my three years has been gone and I became a 9th grade student. 
From my childhood I like to read science fictions and magazines, one day when I was looking through the pages of a magazine a face suddenly struck me. With no time I identify that she is the same girl who comes in my dreams because I can’t forget her beautiful eyes, sizzling smile and floating feathery hair more over her face has been already scribed in my heart.
Is that hard for finding an angel even if she is in a crowd? No, and I just find her and I just put the magazine of and start dancing and jump like a crazy monkey as i at least found ‘she is not only my dream girl but also she is living in the same world where I am living’. My happiness at that time where uncontrollable and my cells and body become super energetic than ever and at that time I even lift a 100 kg.
After some moment I eagerly pick up the magazine and pick the page I see her. Its an article concerning students findings in mathematics, one of the craziest subject I ever hate in my childhood. I read each and every word in that article carefully. Hurray!!! finally I did find her name. !! .
“ Ishana” my dream girl. I said her name along with me just like a 3 year child studying a word
“Ishana.Prajwol” its really matching too. I thank my mom for putting me such a name which is very much matching with her.
I take her photo in the magazine in my mobile cam and keep watching it day and night. My love for her keep increasing day by day and started to think of how to get her as mine. This really get affected in my studies and failures in examination become my partner, everyone started asking me “what is going on in my mind?” teasing from my parents became my daily routine.
At last I understand something that “just dreaming and simply watching will not gain me anything” so I decided to take some strong decisions, for that I need some perfect planning. I spend the next few days for life planning. Its really crazy that a 14 year boy planning about his life. But I don’t take it as a matter, I just make a perfect plan. As a part of my plan I decided to study maths as it is her favorite subject. So i started going for extra classes and spend much time in studies than dreaming. Even though I put her photo in front of me as it’s the only motivating thing that leads my life.
Days passed and my 9th grade annual examination has started. Every day I go for examination after seeing her and the day will surely a wonderful one after seeing his smiling face. At last I completed my 9th examination and it’s the time for enjoyment!! Yah my vacation has started. In this vacation I have some plans in my mind which has to be done. I heard girls love music, as my voice is not so sweet I quit singing and join in violin classes as it is the master instrument which makes strong feelings in mind. I am little bubbly at that time, how a sweet girl like a bubbly guy so I started going for body building center for making my body strong and fit. Sometimes during the pains in my hard work, I even think how crazy I am for doing these kind of things for a girl I have never seen in my life. I don’t even know where she is and what she is doing or did I ever get a chance to meet her. These all thoughts makes so much cracks in my mind but I never give up.
I strongly believe that every work has surely a result. I know god will surely gives a way.so I continue to work with my plan. After one month my 9th grade result has come and I got 90% marks in all subject, now everyone who tease me has started to say good about me. They don’t know the reason behind my success is Ishana.

Odpowiedzi

1. Kochasz tę osobę.

2. Jeżeli wybrałaś /eś:

Czerwony ? twoje życie jest pełne miłości.
Czarny ? jesteś konserwatywna /y i agresywna /y.
Zielony ? twoja dusza jest zrelaksowana i jesteś osobą na luzie.
Niebieski ? jesteś spontaniczna /y i kochasz całusy i pieszczoty tych, których kochasz.
Żółty- jesteś bardzo szczęśliwą osobą i udzielasz dobrych rad tym, którzy są w dołku.

3. Jeżeli pierwsza litera twojego imienia jest:

A-K - masz w sobie dużo miłości, którą ofiarujesz bliskim i przyjaciołom.

L-R - Próbujesz cieszyć się życiem na maxa a twoje życie uczuciowe wkrótce rozkwitnie.

S-Z - lubisz pomagać innym a twoje przyszłe życie uczuciowe wygląda bardzo dobrze.

4. Jeśli urodziłaś /eś się w:

Styczeń ? Marzec
Rok minie ci bardzo dobrze i odkryjesz, że zakochasz się w kimś zupełnie nie oczekiwanym.

Kwiecień - czerwiec

Lipiec- wrzesień
Będziesz mieć wspaniały rok i doświadczysz dużą zmianę w życiu na lepsze.

Październik ? grudzień

Biały : Będziesz mieć przyjaciela, któremu można będzie całkowicie zaufać i zrobiłby dla ciebie wszystko, ale ty możesz sobie z tego nie zdawać sprawy.

6. Ta osoba jest twoim najlepszym przyjacielem.

7. To jest ilość twoich bliskich przyjaciół w twoim życiu.

Jezioro: Jesteś lojalnym przyjacielem i kochanką /iem.

Morze: Jesteś bardzo spontaniczna /y i lubisz zadowalać ludzi.

Chapter-1
My Dream Girl
Do you believe in destiny? If yes it is okay but if you don’t believe then this story will surely change your concepts because this a real evidence of destiny, a living evidence.
My story begin when I was in 6th std. Till that time my life goes quite naturally but that days makes a lot of change in me. Just like every guys in my age I also feel some sort of attraction to a girl, but “what special from others is” she is only my ‘dream girl’.
Every day she comes into my dreams. She sat beside me, talk with me and even laugh with me. That makes me start loving nights more than my days. I patiently put of the days for my beautiful nights. In that way my three years has been gone and I became a 9th grade student. 
From my childhood I like to read science fictions and magazines, one day when I was looking through the pages of a magazine a face suddenly struck me. With no time I identify that she is the same girl who comes in my dreams because I can’t forget her beautiful eyes, sizzling smile and floating feathery hair more over her face has been already scribed in my heart.
Is that hard for finding an angel even if she is in a crowd? No, and I just find her and I just put the magazine of and start dancing and jump like a crazy monkey as i at least found ‘she is not only my dream girl but also she is living in the same world where I am living’. My happiness at that time where uncontrollable and my cells and body become super energetic than ever and at that time I even lift a 100 kg.
After some moment I eagerly pick up the magazine and pick the page I see her. Its an article concerning students findings in mathematics, one of the craziest subject I ever hate in my childhood. I read each and every word in that article carefully. Hurray!!! finally I did find her name. !! .
“ Ishana” my dream girl. I said her name along with me just like a 3 year child studying a word
“Ishana.Prajwol” its really matching too. I thank my mom for putting me such a name which is very much matching with her.
I take her photo in the magazine in my mobile cam and keep watching it day and night. My love for her keep increasing day by day and started to think of how to get her as mine. This really get affected in my studies and failures in examination become my partner, everyone started asking me “what is going on in my mind?” teasing from my parents became my daily routine.
At last I understand something that “just dreaming and simply watching will not gain me anything” so I decided to take some strong decisions, for that I need some perfect planning. I spend the next few days for life planning. Its really crazy that a 14 year boy planning about his life. But I don’t take it as a matter, I just make a perfect plan. As a part of my plan I decided to study maths as it is her favorite subject. So i started going for extra classes and spend much time in studies than dreaming. Even though I put her photo in front of me as it’s the only motivating thing that leads my life.
Days passed and my 9th grade annual examination has started. Every day I go for examination after seeing her and the day will surely a wonderful one after seeing his smiling face. At last I completed my 9th examination and it’s the time for enjoyment!! Yah my vacation has started. In this vacation I have some plans in my mind which has to be done. I heard girls love music, as my voice is not so sweet I quit singing and join in violin classes as it is the master instrument which makes strong feelings in mind. I am little bubbly at that time, how a sweet girl like a bubbly guy so I started going for body building center for making my body strong and fit. Sometimes during the pains in my hard work, I even think how crazy I am for doing these kind of things for a girl I have never seen in my life. I don’t even know where she is and what she is doing or did I ever get a chance to meet her. These all thoughts makes so much cracks in my mind but I never give up.
I strongly believe that every work has surely a result. I know god will surely gives a way.so I continue to work with my plan. After one month my 9th grade result has come and I got 90% marks in all subject, now everyone who tease me has started to say good about me. They don’t know the reason behind my success is Ishana.

Chapter-1
My Dream Girl
Do you believe in destiny? If yes it is okay but if you don’t believe then this story will surely change your concepts because this a real evidence of destiny, a living evidence.
My story begin when I was in 6th std. Till that time my life goes quite naturally but that days makes a lot of change in me. Just like every guys in my age I also feel some sort of attraction to a girl, but “what special from others is” she is only my ‘dream girl’.
Every day she comes into my dreams. She sat beside me, talk with me and even laugh with me. That makes me start loving nights more than my days. I patiently put of the days for my beautiful nights. In that way my three years has been gone and I became a 9th grade student. 
From my childhood I like to read science fictions and magazines, one day when I was looking through the pages of a magazine a face suddenly struck me. With no time I identify that she is the same girl who comes in my dreams because I can’t forget her beautiful eyes, sizzling smile and floating feathery hair more over her face has been already scribed in my heart.
Is that hard for finding an angel even if she is in a crowd? No, and I just find her and I just put the magazine of and start dancing and jump like a crazy monkey as i at least found ‘she is not only my dream girl but also she is living in the same world where I am living’. My happiness at that time where uncontrollable and my cells and body become super energetic than ever and at that time I even lift a 100 kg.
After some moment I eagerly pick up the magazine and pick the page I see her. Its an article concerning students findings in mathematics, one of the craziest subject I ever hate in my childhood. I read each and every word in that article carefully. Hurray!!! finally I did find her name. !! .
“ Ishana” my dream girl. I said her name along with me just like a 3 year child studying a word
“Ishana.Prajwol” its really matching too. I thank my mom for putting me such a name which is very much matching with her.
I take her photo in the magazine in my mobile cam and keep watching it day and night. My love for her keep increasing day by day and started to think of how to get her as mine. This really get affected in my studies and failures in examination become my partner, everyone started asking me “what is going on in my mind?” teasing from my parents became my daily routine.
At last I understand something that “just dreaming and simply watching will not gain me anything” so I decided to take some strong decisions, for that I need some perfect planning. I spend the next few days for life planning. Its really crazy that a 14 year boy planning about his life. But I don’t take it as a matter, I just make a perfect plan. As a part of my plan I decided to study maths as it is her favorite subject. So i started going for extra classes and spend much time in studies than dreaming. Even though I put her photo in front of me as it’s the only motivating thing that leads my life.
Days passed and my 9th grade annual examination has started. Every day I go for examination after seeing her and the day will surely a wonderful one after seeing his smiling face. At last I completed my 9th examination and it’s the time for enjoyment!! Yah my vacation has started. In this vacation I have some plans in my mind which has to be done. I heard girls love music, as my voice is not so sweet I quit singing and join in violin classes as it is the master instrument which makes strong feelings in mind. I am little bubbly at that time, how a sweet girl like a bubbly guy so I started going for body building center for making my body strong and fit. Sometimes during the pains in my hard work, I even think how crazy I am for doing these kind of things for a girl I have never seen in my life. I don’t even know where she is and what she is doing or did I ever get a chance to meet her. These all thoughts makes so much cracks in my mind but I never give up.
I strongly believe that every work has surely a result. I know god will surely gives a way.so I continue to work with my plan. After one month my 9th grade result has come and I got 90% marks in all subject, now everyone who tease me has started to say good about me. They don’t know the reason behind my success is Ishana.

Styczeń ? Marzec

Lipiec- wrzesień
Będziesz mieć wspaniały rok i doświadczysz dużą zmianę w życiu na lepsze.

Październik ? grudzień
Twoje życie uczuciowe nie będzie zbyt wspaniałe, ale w końcu odnajdziesz swoją bratnią duszę.

Jezioro: Jesteś lojalnym przyjacielem i kochanką /iem.

Morze: Jesteś bardzo spontaniczna /y i lubisz zadowalać ludzi.

Chapter-1
My Dream Girl
Do you believe in destiny? If yes it is okay but if you don’t believe then this story will surely change your concepts because this a real evidence of destiny, a living evidence.
My story begin when I was in 6th std. Till that time my life goes quite naturally but that days makes a lot of change in me. Just like every guys in my age I also feel some sort of attraction to a girl, but “what special from others is” she is only my ‘dream girl’.
Every day she comes into my dreams. She sat beside me, talk with me and even laugh with me. That makes me start loving nights more than my days. I patiently put of the days for my beautiful nights. In that way my three years has been gone and I became a 9th grade student. 
From my childhood I like to read science fictions and magazines, one day when I was looking through the pages of a magazine a face suddenly struck me. With no time I identify that she is the same girl who comes in my dreams because I can’t forget her beautiful eyes, sizzling smile and floating feathery hair more over her face has been already scribed in my heart.
Is that hard for finding an angel even if she is in a crowd? No, and I just find her and I just put the magazine of and start dancing and jump like a crazy monkey as i at least found ‘she is not only my dream girl but also she is living in the same world where I am living’. My happiness at that time where uncontrollable and my cells and body become super energetic than ever and at that time I even lift a 100 kg.
After some moment I eagerly pick up the magazine and pick the page I see her. Its an article concerning students findings in mathematics, one of the craziest subject I ever hate in my childhood. I read each and every word in that article carefully. Hurray!!! finally I did find her name. !! .
“ Ishana” my dream girl. I said her name along with me just like a 3 year child studying a word
“Ishana.Prajwol” its really matching too. I thank my mom for putting me such a name which is very much matching with her.
I take her photo in the magazine in my mobile cam and keep watching it day and night. My love for her keep increasing day by day and started to think of how to get her as mine. This really get affected in my studies and failures in examination become my partner, everyone started asking me “what is going on in my mind?” teasing from my parents became my daily routine.
At last I understand something that “just dreaming and simply watching will not gain me anything” so I decided to take some strong decisions, for that I need some perfect planning. I spend the next few days for life planning. Its really crazy that a 14 year boy planning about his life. But I don’t take it as a matter, I just make a perfect plan. As a part of my plan I decided to study maths as it is her favorite subject. So i started going for extra classes and spend much time in studies than dreaming. Even though I put her photo in front of me as it’s the only motivating thing that leads my life.
Days passed and my 9th grade annual examination has started. Every day I go for examination after seeing her and the day will surely a wonderful one after seeing his smiling face. At last I completed my 9th examination and it’s the time for enjoyment!! Yah my vacation has started. In this vacation I have some plans in my mind which has to be done. I heard girls love music, as my voice is not so sweet I quit singing and join in violin classes as it is the master instrument which makes strong feelings in mind. I am little bubbly at that time, how a sweet girl like a bubbly guy so I started going for body building center for making my body strong and fit. Sometimes during the pains in my hard work, I even think how crazy I am for doing these kind of things for a girl I have never seen in my life. I don’t even know where she is and what she is doing or did I ever get a chance to meet her. These all thoughts makes so much cracks in my mind but I never give up.
I strongly believe that every work has surely a result. I know god will surely gives a way.so I continue to work with my plan. After one month my 9th grade result has come and I got 90% marks in all subject, now everyone who tease me has started to say good about me. They don’t know the reason behind my success is Ishana.
